Name:          Nikola Tesla
Lived:         1856 - 1943
Nationality:   Serbian-American
Field:         Engineering
Known For:     AC electricity, induction motor
Contribution:  Alternating current power systems; Tesla coil; radio foundation
Quote:         "The present is theirs; the future is mine."

Name:          Marie Curie
Lived:         1867 - 1934
Nationality:   Polish-French
Field:         Chemistry/Physics
Known For:     Radioactivity
Contribution:  First woman Nobel laureate; Nobel in two sciences; discovered radium and polonium
Quote:         "Nothing in life is to be feared, only to be understood."

